But Erin was gonna come on the podcastand tell me what happened that night.

02:45.249 --> 02:46.291
Really?

02:46.375 --> 02:50.712
All right, so Lanie makes it seemlike Erin is freaking out

02:50.796 --> 02:53.799
because you're about to dredge upa whole bunch of shit.

