<i>No, it's too late.</i>

03:39.678 --> 03:42.806
Listen, if I die before my mother does,

03:42.890 --> 03:45.434
you have to promise methat you keep this from her.

03:45.517 --> 03:47.644
<i>Don't talk like that.I'm gonna get you out.</i>

