-I'm calling the warden.-Poppy.

03:54.151 --> 03:55.652
This one's for Kuvney.

03:56.361 --> 03:59.072
-<i>Warren. Warren.</i>-Piece of shit!

03:59.156 --> 04:00.490
Warren.

04:07.039 --> 04:08.498
She called me,

04:09.208 --> 04:12.503
slurring her words,ranting about Poppy Parnell.

04:12.586 --> 04:15.339
