04:26.850 --> 04:29.853
No way. You don't understand.

04:30.687 --> 04:32.814
We were gonna start over.

04:32.898 --> 04:35.067
Both of us, here, together.

04:36.401 --> 04:37.945
Why were you there?

04:38.487 --> 04:39.530
What do you mean?

04:39.613 --> 04:41.865
Why did she call you and not me?

