05:00.551 --> 05:01.552
Oh, my God.

05:01.635 --> 05:03.178
Josie, I didn't mean it--

05:06.306 --> 05:07.808
<i>Don't tell Mom, okay?</i>

05:14.147 --> 05:15.732
Hey, are you okay?

05:16.233 --> 05:17.901
Josie, are you okay?

05:21.572 --> 05:23.323
Get back to me by end of day.

05:25.200 --> 05:26.743
I need your help.

05:27.452 --> 05:29.288
-With?-Lanie Buhrman.

05:29.371 --> 05:34.042
She was institutionalized and I thinkher time inside holds some of the answers.

05:34.126 --> 05:36.378
Crapped out on that onewith my colleague's wife.

05:36.461 --> 05:39.214
I don't need her medical records,just the name of her doctor.

05:39.298 --> 05:43.552
When I saw you coming in, I thought,"Finally. She's here to talk about us."

05:44.595 --> 05:47.556
-What do you need from me?-The truth which I haven't been getting.

05:47.639 --> 05:49.516
-About?-Come on, Poppy.

05:50.726 --> 05:54.646
You know,Warren and I couldn't be further apart.

05:55.063 --> 05:57.649
But somehow I felt like we were linked.

05:57.733 --> 05:59.568
My destiny with his.

06:00.652 --> 06:04.114
