06:13.207 --> 06:14.958
When you were a kid.

06:16.835 --> 06:21.381
Well, I got some information aboutyour foster mother, Shirley Maxwell.

06:24.384 --> 06:28.013
It said that she drownedwhile you were in her care.

06:28.096 --> 06:29.389
I don't like to talk about it.

06:29.473 --> 06:31.308
Just trying to understand.

06:31.391 --> 06:33.644
She drowned in front of mewhen I was nine.

06:34.770 --> 06:38.315
Just a little under a yearafter my mother died.

06:39.399 --> 06:42.819
Now, I really don't like to think aboutanything from that time.

06:47.241 --> 06:48.992
I couldn't help my mother.

06:51.370 --> 06:52.871
I couldn't help Shirley.

06:52.955 --> 06:55.541
And that's why you've beenso crazed about this case.

06:55.624 --> 06:58.335
Warren is out of time.

06:59.127 --> 07:00.295
And so am I.

07:02.339 --> 07:04.258
I really need your help with Lanie.

07:07.094 --> 07:08.262
I'll see what I can do.

07:09.847 --> 07:10.848
Thank you.

07:12.558 --> 07:14.017
