07:14.852 --> 07:18.230
I got an offer to go backand head up my father's firm in New York.

07:18.313 --> 07:19.356
What? Ingram--

07:19.439 --> 07:24.152
Poppy, I'm helping you on this oneso you can be done with this case,

07:24.236 --> 07:28.198
so you can get back to whatyou used to do, to how we used to be.

07:30.242 --> 07:33.203
That is how we get us back.

07:35.539 --> 07:37.416
You're going down, Warren!

07:41.003 --> 07:42.296
You're a dead man, Cave.

07:42.379 --> 07:43.714
Better watch your back.

07:44.506 --> 07:48.093
Imma watch you spit up, bro.Imma bleed you.

07:49.344 --> 07:51.180
Sleep tight, princess.

07:51.263 --> 07:52.890
You're fucking dead.

07:53.807 --> 07:55.726
I'm gonna fuck you up, Cave.

07:57.060 --> 07:58.812
I'm gonna get you.

08:07.154 --> 08:08.488
What have you got?

08:08.906 --> 08:12.618
