08:12.701 --> 08:15.829
You see less and less of her in theseas the girls get older.

08:16.246 --> 08:18.248
There's plenty of Erin and Josie.

08:18.332 --> 08:19.791
Chuck and Josie.

08:19.875 --> 08:21.752
<i>Does it take a picture?Why are you just holding it?</i>

08:21.835 --> 08:23.754
<i>I don't know. I have to...It's still videoing.</i>

08:23.837 --> 08:25.422
