08:27.591 --> 08:29.009
Hold that thought.

08:31.261 --> 08:32.261
Hey, babe, any luck?

08:32.679 --> 08:34.181
<i>Insurance company worked.</i>

08:34.264 --> 08:37.183
<i>Lanie's doctor still works at Redwood.Ian Poole.</i>

08:37.267 --> 08:38.434
Yes.

08:38.519 --> 08:39.561
Thanks so much for this.

08:39.977 --> 08:43.106
Think about moving back to New York.Really think about it.

08:43.815 --> 08:45.734
We'll discuss it later. I promise.

08:45.817 --> 08:47.069
Are you kidding me?

08:47.152 --> 08:50.739
For now, can we just stay focusedon Lanie Buhrman?

08:51.740 --> 08:52.741
Okay.

08:53.867 --> 08:55.035
What next then?

09:34.199 --> 09:36.326
Josie, I'm sorry about your mom.

09:37.744 --> 09:39.580
Are you? Really?

09:40.706 --> 09:42.749
I lost my mother when I was nine.

09:44.126 --> 09:48.463
And I still think about her every day.And it still breaks my heart.

09:48.547 --> 09:51.008
My mom died of an overdose

09:51.091 --> 09:54.928
right around the time you were convincingthe world that she might be a murderer.

09:55.762 --> 09:57.639
What could be better for your podcast?

09:57.723 --> 09:59.016
Finding out the truth.

10:00.142 --> 10:03.145
I was going to see your motherwhen she died.

10:03.228 --> 10:04.396
Why?

10:05.397 --> 10:06.940
She was going to talk.

10:07.024 --> 10:09.526
When I arrived at your aunt Susan's,

10:09.610 --> 10:12.654
the paramedics were there and your sister.

10:13.447 --> 10:18.619
Your mother was on a rehab drugcalled Antabuse the night of the murder.

10:19.119 --> 10:21.330
She wasn't passed out drunkat the party, Josie,

10:21.413 --> 10:23.332
she wasn't even drinking that night.

10:26.126 --> 10:28.170
But you knew that, didn't you?

10:28.962 --> 10:31.340
She never got the chanceto tell me what she knew.

10:32.216 --> 10:34.635
-And I don't think it was an accident.-No.

10:34.718 --> 10:36.220
Your sister's the one who found the body.

10:36.303 --> 10:38.514
Your sister's the oneyour mother supposedly called.

10:38.597 --> 10:39.598
Stop.

10:39.681 --> 10:42.768
