10:42.851 --> 10:45.229
-It was calibrated perfectly to be---We're done.

10:45.312 --> 10:47.189
I think Lanie killed your father.

10:48.941 --> 10:52.528
And when she found out your mother wasgoing to come clean, she killed her too.

10:54.947 --> 10:57.658
You're the only one left, Josie.

10:58.534 --> 11:01.537
Seventeen years,you cut yourself off from her.

11:04.289 --> 11:07.167
Changed your name,made sure she couldn't reach you.

11:08.168 --> 11:09.211
Just let go.

11:09.294 --> 11:10.379
<i>What are you doing? Lanie...</i>

11:10.462 --> 11:14.299
If there is even a tiny part of youthat believes any of this could be true,

11:14.383 --> 11:15.801
then you've got to help me.

11:18.595 --> 11:20.347
What do you want me to do?

11:28.564 --> 11:30.023
-Can I help you?-Yes.

11:30.107 --> 11:32.985
I am here to pick up my juvenile records.

11:33.443 --> 11:35.279
The release was authorized by Dr. Poole.

11:35.362 --> 11:37.865
-And your name?-Lanie Buhrman.

11:41.118 --> 11:42.286
Dr. Poole.

11:42.369 --> 11:44.621
It's good to see you looking so well.

11:45.038 --> 11:46.456
How have you been?

11:46.540 --> 11:48.250
I've been great.

11:48.750 --> 11:51.628
I'm married.I have a four-year-old daughter.

11:51.712 --> 11:53.589
I understand you need your records?

11:53.672 --> 11:55.632
Yes. I'm applying for a job.

11:56.175 --> 11:57.259
Children services.

11:57.342 --> 12:01.180
