12:01.263 --> 12:03.557
including records from my time here.

12:03.640 --> 12:04.892
Good for you.

12:04.975 --> 12:06.351
Michael can help you.

12:07.227 --> 12:09.396
I am thrilled to see you happy, Lanie.

12:11.106 --> 12:12.107
Thank you.

12:16.403 --> 12:18.447
Lanie, we need to talk.

12:18.947 --> 12:21.992
Sure, I'm just finishingMr. Carr's death certificate.

12:22.075 --> 12:24.244
Rosemary can finish that.

12:26.580 --> 12:31.960
So, a few troubling revelations have cometo light over the past few weeks.

12:32.044 --> 12:34.087
What revelations?

