-Oh, my God.-What is it, Josie?

23:39.086 --> 23:42.172
It... It was me.

23:45.759 --> 23:47.678
It was me.

23:59.106 --> 24:01.733
Well, you huffed and you puffedand you blew the house down.

24:01.817 --> 24:03.151
For what? For nothing.

24:03.235 --> 24:04.695
Warren will go free.

24:04.778 --> 24:08.615
Yeah, and sweet, innocent,good twin Josie'll take his place.

24:08.949 --> 24:12.578
Imagine what's gonna happen to herin there because of you.

