All because you couldn't mindyour own goddamn business.

24:15.455 --> 24:17.666
If I had to go, it might be okay.

24:17.749 --> 24:20.669
But Josie? She's gonna get eaten alive.

24:21.128 --> 24:23.755
She's the weak twin. There's always one.

24:23.839 --> 24:26.008
